{"tid":1868562,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利記數據勁過3冠曼聯「不敗」阿仙奴","createTime":"2020-02-07T15:57:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T17:17:21.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7ab8b7f267d522efcb221929ba203eeded3a68d6","tid":1868562,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T15:57:56.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】英國《太陽報》作出統計，指正邁向30年來首個頂級聯賽冠軍的利物浦，數據上比當年曼聯3冠王及阿仙奴的不敗球季還要出色，是英超28季以來最具統治力的球隊。<br />\n<br />\n英國《太陽報》近日作出統計，指正邁向30年來首個頂級聯賽冠軍的利物浦，現時的表現比當年曼聯3冠王及阿仙奴的不敗球季還要出色，是英超28季以來最具統治力的球隊。<br />\n<br />\n若要數英超史上最偉大球隊，相信很多球迷會拿1998/99年球季的曼聯及2003/04年球季的阿仙奴作比較，但相信今季過後，隨時有更多人談論這支正力圖打破過往任何紀錄的利物浦。<br />\n<br />\n紅軍於25輪英超過後，除在聯賽榜以22分大幅拋離排次席的曼城外，其73分的成績，更遠比當年阿仙奴於不敗球季同期的61分更加優勝，而60個入球也剛好比曼聯於3冠王球季同期攻入的59球為多。<br />\n<br />\n利物浦中場佐敦軒達臣及雲拿當的級數，不一定可媲美當年曼聯的史高斯及碧咸，又或者費明奴及法賓奴的名氣及當年阿仙奴的伯金及韋拉，不過在領隊高普運用得宜，加上傷兵問題未算嚴重下，球隊就打出了現時的無敵表現。<br />\n<br />\n多支英超隊暫時休戰，利物浦到下周六才作客諾域治，只要於這支榜尾球隊身上全取3分，就能提早12輪鎖定聯賽前4的來季歐聯資格。更重要的是，紅軍在餘下13場比賽再增添多6場勝利的話，便可提早宣佈封王，贏得球隊自1990年以來首個頂級聯賽冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"e214f75e7bd69eb28371266766341a4b07182a9b","tid":1868562,"uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T16:00:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/6906ac3202c21a3cb922983a1177d834/756cd901857c12f5-86/s400x600/8ffe2ca3ce04bb95fb9f5c408a037efd54239d53.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F6906ac3202c21a3cb922983a1177d834%2F756cd901857c12f5-86%2Fs400x600%2F8ffe2ca3ce04bb95fb9f5c408a037efd54239d53.gifv&h=63d965ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/c212b17eff6438173471f9c90aa5946a/756cd901857c12f5-01/s400x600/74f3d3c5eec5a8e5cbc883daa7c3b3a928beee0a.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Fc212b17eff6438173471f9c90aa5946a%2F756cd901857c12f5-01%2Fs400x600%2F74f3d3c5eec5a8e5cbc883daa7c3b3a928beee0a.gifv&h=8f4fb373&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/ac1bcd82144383f6174ea51a4b68c23b/756cd901857c12f5-e0/s400x600/125fa9e1c036f441dcb922e4b11284f2bb7e61ba.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Fac1bcd82144383f6174ea51a4b68c23b%2F756cd901857c12f5-e0%2Fs400x600%2F125fa9e1c036f441dcb922e4b11284f2bb7e61ba.gifv&h=d82630b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c019ab213da04bbcfbb208a969697926d0c076","tid":1868562,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T16:04:21.000Z","msg":"過到馬體會再算"},{"pid":"d17303be292fb136b6c0eda13e2fde3e235b8e26","tid":1868562,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T16:28:15.000Z","msg":"點解今周冇得踢"},{"pid":"df4177a01eec5186f09040ca2ac282d1aa9440af","tid":1868562,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T16:42:57.000Z","msg":"利物浦到下周六才作客諾域治，只要於這支榜尾球隊身上全取3分，就能提早12輪鎖定聯賽前4的來季歐聯資格。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b827d29967a29ef3b9e2cffe84e38423f62f74e6","tid":1868562,"uid":194415,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T16:47:36.000Z","msg":"拎左 三冠未？未<br />\n全季不敗嬴英超未？未<br />\n<br />\n做到再講都唔遲"},{"pid":"d6d8cfa6c90a63252ffa1c9e3a5f7ad56d987e60","tid":1868562,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d17303be292fb136b6c0eda13e2fde3e235b8e26","tid":1868562,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T16:28:15.000Z","msg":"點解今周冇得踢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T16:51:21.000Z","msg":"蓋Ching 一本道係邊個來"},{"pid":"18b3629a1881337b3c46062